document_api_meta.title: Get Warehouse List
document_api_meta.env_desc: This API retrieves all warehouse information associated with the seller. Warehouse information includes name, status, address, and other details.

request_header_param.name: x-tts-access-token
request_header_param.desc: The seller access_token value from [Get Access Token](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3292b0f40314a92d75#Get%20Access%20Token%20API), when user_type = 0. Follow this [guide](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a344ddec3030b238fa0) to get seller access_token.

request_query_param.name: app_key
request_query_param.desc: Every single app will have a unique key. Please use the specific key assigned to your app.

request_query_param.name: sign
request_query_param.desc: Signature generated by gen algorithm. When you send API requests to TTS, you must sign them so that TTS can identify the senders.

request_query_param.name: timestamp
request_query_param.desc: Unix timestamp GMT (UTC+00:00). This timestamp is used across all API requests. Developers can use this convert to local time.

request_query_param.name: shop_cipher
request_query_param.desc:
Use this property to pass shop information in requesting the API. Failure in passing the correct value when requesting the API for cross-border shops will return incorrect response. 
Get by API [Get Authorization Shop](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9?external_id=6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9)

response_param.name: code
response_param.desc: The success or failure status code returned in API response.

response_param.name: message
response_param.desc: The success or failure messages returned in API response. Reasons of failure will be described in the message.

response_param.name: request_id
response_param.desc: Request log

response_param.name: data
response_param.desc: Specific return information

response_param.name: ^warehouses
response_param.desc: All the warehouses associated with the seller.

response_param.name: ^^id
response_param.desc: The warehouse ID, a unique and immutable primary key, used for all warehouse logistics.

response_param.name: ^^entity_id
response_param.desc: The warehouse entity ID, used to associate physical information of a warehouse, different warehouses may be associated with the same entity.

response_param.name: ^^name
response_param.desc: Warehouse name. This name is not unique across the TikTok Shop system.

response_param.name: ^^effect_status
response_param.desc:
Possible values:
- ENABLED: All products in stock are available for sale.
- DISABLED: All products in stock are unavailable for sale. 
- RESTRICTED: The warehouse is either on "holiday mode" or "order limit mode." All products in stock are unavailable for sale.
-Holiday mode: When the seller cannot fulfill an order from a warehouse, the seller can turn on holiday mode for the warehouse in seller center. 
- Order limit mode: When the seller violates TikTok Shop policies, TikTok Shop will limit the order volume that can be fulfilled by a warehouse.

response_param.name: ^^type
response_param.desc:
Possible values:
- SALES_WAREHOUSE: Warehouse for shipping products.  
- RETURN_WAREHOUSE: Warehouse for receiving returned products. 
You can have the same warehouse for both shipping and receiving returns, but they will have different warehouse IDs with the same address.

response_param.name: ^^sub_type
response_param.desc:
Possible values:
- DOMESTIC_WAREHOUSE: The warehouse is in the same country as the target market and the seller.
- CB_OVERSEA_WAREHOUSE: For cross-border sellers, a local warehouse in the target market. 
- CB_DIRECT_SHIPPING_WAREHOUSE: For cross-border sellers, a warehouse in the seller's base country, e.g., Mainland China or Hong Kong.

response_param.name: ^^is_default
response_param.desc: The default warehouse.  If a product is listed with no designated warehouse, the default warehouse will be used.

response_param.name: ^^address
response_param.desc: Warehouse address.

response_param.name: ^^^region
response_param.desc: Warehouse region.

response_param.name: ^^^state
response_param.desc: Warehouse state or province.

response_param.name: ^^^city
response_param.desc: Warehouse city.

response_param.name: ^^^distict
response_param.desc: Warehouse district.

response_param.name: ^^^town
response_param.desc: Warehouse town.

response_param.name: ^^^contact_person
response_param.desc: Warehouse contact person name.

response_param.name: ^^^first_name
response_param.desc:
Kanji first name
Applicable only for the JP market.

response_param.name: ^^^last_name
response_param.desc:
Kanji last name
Applicable only for the JP market.

response_param.name: ^^^first_name_local_script
response_param.desc:
Hiragana or Katakana first name
Applicable only for the JP market.

response_param.name: ^^^last_name_local_script
response_param.desc:
Hiragana or Katakana last name
Applicable only for the JP market.

response_param.name: ^^^postal_code
response_param.desc: Warehouse address postal code (also known as zip code)

response_param.name: ^^^full_address
response_param.desc: The combined warehouse address, including the street address and other address information such as apartment number, building, floor..etc (optional)

response_param.name: ^^^region_code
response_param.desc: Warehouse region code.

response_param.name: ^^^phone_number
response_param.desc: Warehouse phone number.

response_param.name: ^^^address_line1
response_param.desc:
The first line of the warehouse address, like street name and street number.
Note: 
- For Brazilian market, this represents the neighborhood or district.
- For the JP market, this represents the district (Chome), block (Banchi), building number (Go).

response_param.name: ^^^address_line2
response_param.desc:
The second line of the warehouse address, like flat, apartment, or suit.
Note: For the Brazilian market, this represents the street name.

response_param.name: ^^^address_line3
response_param.desc:
This represents the street number. If it's `s/n`, it means null.
Note: Available only in the Brazilian market.

response_param.name: ^^^address_line4
response_param.desc:
This represents supplement information, like flat, apartment, or suit (optional).
Note: Available only in the Brazilian market.

response_param.name: ^^^geolocation
response_param.desc: The geographical location of the address.

response_param.name: ^^^^latitude
response_param.desc: The latitude of the address.

response_param.name: ^^^^longitude
response_param.desc: The longitude of the address.

error_code_list.msg: Internal error. Please try again. If the issue persists after multiple attempts, please contact platform support.
